- Maintain the project structure:
  - `src/components`: React components and react three fiber components
  - `src/shaders`: Shader files.
  - `src/store`: State management (e.g., `gameStore.ts`).
  - `src/types`: TypeScript definitions.
  - `src/utils`: Utility functions.
  - `public/models`: 3D models (`.gltf`, `.bin`).
  - `public/images`: Textures, images.
  - `public/sounds`: Audio files.